Welcome to your dream home at Woodfield Country Club, a residence that seamlessly blends modern luxury with timeless elegance. This completely renovated property showcases meticulous attention to detail, creating a captivating atmosphere of sophistication.Immerse yourself in the exquisite features of this home, starting with the complete renovation that has touched every corner, providing a fresh and contemporary look throughout. The heart of this home, the chef's kitchen, boasts a 10 ft Panda marble island and high-end Thermador Welcome to your dream home at Woodfield Country Club, a residence that seamlessly blends modern luxury with timeless elegance. Recently renovated in 2021, this property showcases meticulous attention to detail, creating a captivating atmosphere of sophistication.

Immerse yourself in the exquisite features of this home, starting with the complete renovation that has touched every corner, providing a fresh and contemporary look throughout. The addition of a new roof not only enhances the aesthetic appeal but also ensures peace of mind with its beauty and durability.

Experience elevated security and energy efficiency with the installation of top-of-the-line impact windows. The heart of this home, the chef's kitchen, boasts a 10 ft Panda marble island and high-end Thermador appliances, catering to culinary enthusiasts and creating a central hub for gatherings.

Stay cool and comfortable year-round with the state-of-the-art A/C, featuring advanced UV technology. Sleek and stylish porcelain floors seamlessly connect the living spaces, creating a cohesive and modern aesthetic.

Indulge in a spa-like experience in the newly renovated bathrooms, and retreat to your own secluded oasis in the first-floor primary suite with a private retreat area. The courtyard, recently revamped in 2023, beckons with a sparkling pool, sun deck, and spa, offering a perfect outdoor escape.

Worry-free maintenance is guaranteed with brand new pool equipment, ensuring your enjoyment of the heated saltwater pool. This home is move-in ready, inviting you to embrace the South Florida lifestyle effortlessly.

Don't miss the opportunity to call this exceptional property your own. Come see it today and immerse yourself in the epitome of luxury living at Woodfield Country Club!
